Forum plugin for SquirrelMail
=============================

1. Requirements
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

   * PHP version 4.3.2 or above.
   * PEAR extension with MDB2 package and MDB2 Driver.
   * A database.


2. Installation instructions
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

   See INSTALL for installation instructions.


3. Upgrade instructions
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

   1.0 to 1.1 
    - Just replace old plugin directory with the new downloaded.


